# Zaniel
>tag

Zaniel was a wild [[Races/Dragon\|dragon]], with teal green scales. He was known as the fastest dragon for generations, and often boasts that he could beat [[Dragons/Arion\|Arion]] if only he had a body still. 

He was very fond of [[Characters/Cecilé Dragonsong\|Cecilé Dragonsong]] and acted almost as if he were her bonded dragon, despite the fact that she was never actually a [[Races/Dragon Rider\|Rider]].

[[Dragons/Eldfyrn\|Eldfyrn]] was his elder brother, whose egg was given to the Riders. Despite his status as a bonded dragon, he and Zaniel still had a close relationship.
